'''天主教波尔多总教区'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Burdigalensis}}；{{lang-fr|Archidiocèse de Bordeaux}}）是[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]在[[法国|法国]]西南部设立的一个总教区。此總教區以主教座堂驻地[[波尔多|波尔多]]命名。范围相当于[[吉伦特省|吉伦特省]]，而波尔多教省相当于[[阿基坦|阿基坦]]大区。 

{{clarify|於4世紀升為總教區。|post-text=：甚麼於4世紀升為總教區？}}總教區於2006年時有1,089,457名教友（佔轄區總人口80.0%）、593個[[堂區|堂區]]和298名[[司鐸|司鐸]]。現任總主教為{{link-fr|若望-保祿·雅默斯|Jean-Paul James}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 14.11.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/14/191114b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-11-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191114143026/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/14/191114b.html |archivedate=2019-11-14 |language=en |date=2019-11-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-fr|培特朗·拉孔貝|Bertrand Lacombe}}和{{link-fr|若望-瑪利亞·雷-弗爾|Jean-Marie Le Vert}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Other Pontifical Acts, 14.04.2016 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2016/04/14/160414d.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-10-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191001133732/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2016/04/14/160414d.html |archivedate=2019-10-01 |language=en |date=2016-04-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 09.03.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/03/09/180309c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-10-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191001134830/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/03/09/180309c.html |archivedate=2019-10-01 |language=en |date=2018-03-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為[[若望-伯多祿·里卡爾|若望-伯多祿·里卡爾]][[樞機|樞機]]<ref name="Vatican20191001">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 01.10.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/10/01/191001a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-10-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191001123519/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/10/01/191001a.html |archivedate=2019-10-01 |language=en |date=2019-10-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

